snippet.description:
Inspired by Randy, N5ILQ, I decided to attempt a 5 Park Rove in pursuit of the Warthog Award.  I've never done such a thing, so I mapped out 5 parks I had previously activated and set out to get it done.  In the beginning, things did not go according to the script.  I had antenna system issues in Park #1 which put me way behind schedule. However, in the end, I hammed a little harder and go the rove completed.  It was a whole lot of fun.  Come along for the rid.
